                <h1>Understanding Background Checks: What to Expect</h1>
                <p>A background check typically includes a variety of checks to verify an individual's history and qualifications. Common components are criminal history, employment verification, education verification, credit checks, and reference checks. These checks help employers make informed decisions about potential hires and ensure safety in the workplace.</p>
